Class GASolution

  • java.lang.Object
    • xing.base.adapter.SolutionAdapter
      • xing.base.AsexualSolutionBase

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AsexualSolution, Isomophic<Solution>, Solution
    public class GASolution
extends AsexualSolutionBase
    GA mutation strategy for solving TSP. Each instance produce 4 offsprings. 1 identical copy of the parent itself, 1 shifted version, 1 swapped version, and 1 copy of reversed version.
